rries are \\\"the terrorist threat, drones, and the protest threat, cyber attacks\\\", according Christophe Abad, the military commander for the Paris region.\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.678656202087476e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The biggest worries\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"the terrorist threat\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2526}, {\"ngram\": \"drones\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest threat\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"cyber attacks\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"Christophe Abad\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2601}, {\"ngram\": \"the military commander\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The camp is named after Corporal Alain Mimoun, who joined the army aged 18 and went on to become one of France's greatest athletes, winning Olympic medals in 1948, 1952 and 1956 on the track and in the marathon.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9765811636155369, \"rank\": 0.023958342927939115, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The camp\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"Corporal Alain Mimoun\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"the army\", \"from\": 2707, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic medals\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the request of the heritage and environment departments, the 10-hectare site is fenced off and is designed to blend in to the landscape.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the request\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"the heritage and environment departments\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10-hectare site\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"the landscape\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No building exceeds one storey in height, and each one is set back at least two metres away from protected trees.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No building\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"one storey\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"height\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"each one\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"protected trees\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even the design of the canteen reflects the surrounding pines, beeches and chestnuts.\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even the design\", \"from\": 3118, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"the canteen\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"the surrounding pines\", \"from\": 3158, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"beeches\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"chestnuts\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spread over 5,000 square metres, the canteen has seats for 2,100 hungry soldiers who will consume tonnes of food over the course of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 5,000 square metres\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3236}, {\"ngram\": \"the canteen\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"seats\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"2,100 hungry soldiers\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"tonnes\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3317}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3337, \"to\": 3349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3363}]}]}"